opinions in English;\n* Enhance their pronunciation and intonation skills\nLearn strategies for effective public speaking;\n* Apply English language skills to real-world situations."}, "outline": {"ch": "課程大綱\n第1週：課程介紹\n第2週\n單元1：發音與語調\n* 音標\n* 重音與節奏\n* 語調模式\n* 常見發音錯誤與矯正方法\n第3週：期中考（1）\n第4~5週\n單元2：會話技巧\n* 閒聊與破冰\n* 提問與回答\n* 表達意見與給予回饋\n* 主動聆聽與回應\n第6週：期中考（2）\n第7~8週\n單元3：學術口語\n* 呈現研究成果\n* 參與課堂討論\n* 口頭報告\n* 寫作和發表有效演講\n第9週：期中考（3）\n第10~14週\n單元4：專業口語\n* 面試與人脈建立\n* 電話與線上溝通\n* 商業簡報與會議\n* 談判與說服技巧\n第15週：期末考\n[註] 4月3日為兒童節補假日，不上課。\n課程活動\n* 小組討論\n* 兩人一組練習\n* 角色扮演\n* 口頭報告\n* 口試\n* 課堂評估\n* 同儕評估與回饋", "en": "[Week 1] : Course Introduction\n[weeks 2]\nUnit 1: Pronunciation and Intonation\n* Phonetics and phonology\n* Stress and rhythm\n* Intonation patterns\n* Common pronunciation errors and how to correct them\n[Week 3] : Midterm (1)\n[Weeks 4~5]\nUnit 2: Conversation Skills\n* Small talk and icebreakers\n* Asking and answering questions\n* Expressing opinions and giving feedback\n* Active listening and responding\n[Week 6] : Midterm (2)\n[Weeks 7~8]\nUnit 3: Academic Speaking\n* Presenting research findings\n* Participating in class discussions\n* Giving oral presentations\n* Writing and delivering effective speeches\n[Week 9] : Midterm (3)\n[Weeks 10~14]\nUnit 4: Professional Speaking\n* Job interviews and networking\n* Telephone and online communication\n* Business presentations and meetings\n* Negotiation and persuasion skills\n[Week 15] : Final Exam\n[Note] No class meeting on April 3rd due to the Spring Break\n[Course Activities]\n* Group discussions\n* Pair work\n* Role-plays\n* Presentations\n* Oral exams\n* Assessment\n* Peer evaluation and feedncak"}, "textbook": {"ch": "* 課堂講義\n* 線上教育影片", "en": "* in-class handouts\n* Online educational videos"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n\n個別指導", "en": ["Lecture", "", "", "Individual Instruction"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "* 出席率 10％\n* 期中考 30％ (10％ * 3次)\n* 期末考 20％\n* 課堂練習 40％", "en": "* Attendance 10％\n* Midterms 30％ (10％ * 3 times)\n* Final Exam 20％\n* In class Practice 40％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "周二1400-1450，周三1400-1450，周五中午", "en": "Tue. & Wed. 1400-1450, Fri. 1200-1250"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "期末評量檢討回饋。", "en": "Final evaluation and feedback on students' overall course performance"}, "domain": {"ch": "應用英文", "en": "應用英文"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "語言溝通", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "文化視野", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "自主學習", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "作品/創作展演"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Language & Communication Skills", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance", "Self Assessment/ Peer Assessment", "Products/Creative Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Intercultural Literacy", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Products/Creative Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Self-directed Lifelong Learning", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Products/Creative Performance"]}]}, "assignCriteria": {"ch": ["學制:限學士班。"], "en": ["Type:Undergraduate Program only."]}, "preselecStu": 0, "stuGender": {"male": 0, "Female": 0}, "stuGrade": {"doctor": {}, "master": {}, "bachelor": {}}, "stus": [{"serial": "1", "stunum": "10*******", "department": "資訊管理學系", "grade": "4", "class": "2", "priority": "1", "isRequired": false, "isPreselected": false, "isManuallySelected": false, "isCodeSelected": false}, {"serial": "2", "stunum": "11*******", "department": "英美語文學系", "grade": "4", "class": "*", "priority": "1", "isRequired": false, "isPreselected": false, "isManuallySelected": false, "isCodeSelected": false}, {"serial": "3", "stunum": "11*******", "department": "數學系(數學科學組)", "grade": "4", "class": "1", "priority": "1", "isRequired": false, "isPresele